                <h1>Legendary North Carolina head coach Dean Smith passes away at 83</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/24f7f28a-95c3-4cc4-863a-6607dca3a532.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Former&#x20;North&#x20;Carolina&#x20;head&#x20;coach&#x20;Dean&#x20;Smith&#x20;passed&#x20;away&#x20;Feb.&#x20;7&#x20;at&#x20;his&#x20;home&#x20;in&#x20;Chapel&#x20;Hill." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Former North Carolina head coach Dean Smith passed away Feb. 7 at his home in Chapel Hill.

                            
                        </div>
                    </figure>
                
                                    <div class="row  mt-4 mb-0 mb-md-4">
                        <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
                            <aside class="author-name">
                                    
    
                                    
            By <a href="https://www.dukechronicle.com/staff/nick-martin">Nick Martin</a>
                                    
                                <div class="mt-1">
                                    <span class="can-localize">February 8, 2015 | 4:19pm EST</span>
